Name: basic type
Description: Boilerplate——the debugger knows how to read bit as the type anyway.

Name: range type defined by min and max
Description:
.stabs "name:descriptor (type) type-def=
type-desc type-ref; low-bound; high-bound;", N_LSYM, NIL, NIL, NIL

Name: range type defined by number of bits
Description:
.stabs "name: desc(type) type-def=
type-desc type-ref; bit-count; 0;",
N_LSYM, NIL, NIL, NIL
